# Ignore everything in ~/.claude by default — this directory holds a lot of
# machine-local state (credentials, history, sessions, caches, projects, etc.).
*

# ...except the things worth version-controlling and sharing across machines:
!.gitignore
!README.md
!settings.json
!skills/
!skills/**

# ...but NOT the brot-plan scratch tracker — it's gitignored per the brot skill
# convention (the durable record is the merged PRs; /brot-done deletes it).
skills/BROT_PLAN.md
